values:
thats really the greatest for me to read the announcements of my PRINCESS always after I have bought new flowers for my PRINCESS........

PRINCESS, I promise you, this will be the greatest flowers page on the internet, no store will have more bouquets on their site than you, PRINCESS.....

PRINCESS, this is a wonderful way to show you my love, thank you for this way....

PRINCESS, you know I know only one road and this road leads always to you, PRINCESS, always......
Why do I make the same mistakes over and over? Am I an idiot?  Sometimes, I think so.  PRINCESS tell me what She expects from me and I continue to disappoint.  I am a pathetic slave sometimes.

what a terrible night I had......

big trouble with my PRINCESS, we had some misunderstandings with bad consequences for me, sometimes its really bad that some words content different thoughts in different languages....

Statement:

there are many ways to Ohio, but there is only one way to my PRINCESS, I want go only this way.....
this way means 
I will do everything I can to make my PRINCESS happy 
I will do everything I can to adore my PRINCESS 
I will do everything I can to worship my PRINCESS
I will do everything I can to show the public that I say yes to my PRINCESS
I will do everything I can to show everyone that I belong to my PRINCESS

PRINCESS, this has nothing to do with hypocrisy, if it would be necessary I would give my life for you, my PRINCESS

toiletbrush has been a hypocritical little turd, posting like he is some selfless, 5-star sub...better than the other subs. In actuality, he's just a pig like the rest of you....a pig suffering from delusions of grandeur. After all this week of spouting his lovesick elegies of what a grateful, giving servant he is...he's has the balls to throw a hissy last night because I was too busy to chatter with him. It's time for a trip down memory lane, bitch! Once you were a FAT pig...now you are a medium-sized pig. THANKS TO ME. This is what you are..and ALWAYS will be. *insert harp music* Just another pig #1 Just another pig #2 Just another pig #3 Just another pig #4 he will have lost his privileges until he has atoned for his sins.
